INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(1, "Gran Torino", 8.99, "Drama", "", "Clint Eastwood directs and stars in this drama featuring Korean War veteran Walt Kowalski. He doesn\'t much like how his life or his neighborhood has turned out. He especially doesn\'t like the people next door, Hmong immigrants from Southeast Asia. But events force Walt to defend those neighbors against a local gang that feeds on violence and fear. For the first time since Million Dollar Baby, Clint Eastwood works on both sides of the camera, winning the National Board of Review Award as Best Actor for his bone-deep playing of Kowalski, burnished with experience, grace and gravitas into a prime vintage Eastwood performance.");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(2, "Back to the Future", 9.99, "Science Fiction", "", "In this 1980s sci-fi classic, small-town California teen Marty McFly (Michael J. Fox) is thrown back into the 50s when an experiment by his eccentric scientis friend Doc Brown (Christopher Lloyd) goes awry. Traveling through time in a modified DeLorean car, Marty encounters young versions of his parents (Crispin Glover, Lea Thompson), and must make sure that they fall in love or he\'ll cease to exist. Even more dauntingly, Marty has to return to his own time and save the life of Doc Brown.");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(3, "Fight Club", 12.99, "Thriller", "", "Tired with his life and dead-end job, an insomniac worker named Jack (Edward Norton) attends support groups to find purpose in his life. On the way home from a business trip, he meets soap salesman Tyler Durden (Brad Pitt). After a freak event leaves Jack homeless, he calls Tyler for a place to stay. The two bond quickly and Jack begins seeing things through Tyler\'s eyes and not just his own.");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(4, "Enemy of the State", 7.99, "Thriller", "", "Attorney Robert Clayton Dean (Will Smith) bumps into former college roomate Daniel Zavits (Jason Lee) on the street as Zavits is running from NSA agents. Shortly after seeing him, Zavits is killed, and is questioned about it by NSA agents. Shortly after, Dean\'s life is thrown into disarray as his past is dug up by unknown persons and his relationship with his wife becomes bitter. Soon he finds himself being chased by the NSA, but receives some help from former NSA agent Brill (Gene Hackman). Desperate and with no place to go or hide, Dean fights his pursuers with intelligence of his own. The question is: does Dean have what it takes to win this battle of wits against the NSA?");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(5, "Kiss of the Dragon", 11.99, "Thriller", "", "Chinese intelligence agent Liu Siu-jian (Jet Li) is sent to Paris to help crack a French-Chinese smuggling ring. When the mission goes wrong, he gets embroiled in a conspiracy and is framed for murder. Liu later meets a prostitute named Jessica (Bridget Fonda) who was present when the murder took place. Li teams up with her to protect her from the actual killer and to exonerate himself from the crime.");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(6, "American Beauty", 13.99, "Drama", "", "While struggling to endure his tightly wound wife, an un-fulfilling job and a sullen teenage daughter, suburbanite Lester Burnham (Kevin Spacey) falls deep into a mid-life crisis and becomes infatuated with one of his daughter\'s friends.");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(7, "Lethal Weapon", 8.99, "Action", "", "Roger Murtaugh (Danny Glover) is an aging family man and sensible veteran police officer just trying to make it through the day unscathed. Martin Riggs (Mel Gibson) is a suicidal loose cannon cop who doesn\'t care if he even lives to see the end of the day. Reluctantly thrown together to solve the mysterious murder of a banker\'s daughter, the unlikely duo uncovers a dangerous ring of drug smugglers employing ex-military mercenaries.");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(8, "The Deer Hunter", 10.99, "Drama", "", "Michael (Robert DeNiro), Steven (John Savage), and Nick (Christopher Walken) are young factory workers from Pennsylvania who enlist into the Army to fight in Vietnam. Before they go, Steven marries the pregnant Angela, and their wedding party also serves as the men\'s farewell party. After time served in Vietnam, all three of them return home changed men");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(9, "The Negotiator", 13.99, "Thriller", "", "In the midst of an elaborate conspiracy, expert negotiator Danny Roman (Samuel L. Jackson) is driven to the edge when he is framed for the murder of his partner, as well as embezzling money from his department\'s pension fund. His only chance to prove his innocence is to take hostages himself, acquire the services of another expert negotiator, and find out who\'s running the conspiracy before it is too late.");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(10, "Safe House", 9.99, "Thriller", "", "Matt Weston (Ryan Reynolds) is a CIA rookie who is manning a safe house in Cape Town, South Africa, when Tobin Frost (Denzel Washington) the CIA\'s most wanted rogue agent is captured and taken to the safe house. During Frost\'s interrogation, the safe house is overtaken by mercenaries who want Frost. Weston and Frost escape and must stay out of the gunmen\'s sight until they can get to another safe house.");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(11, "Horrible Bosses", 4.99, "Comedy", "", "Disgruntled buddies Nick (Jason Bateman), Kurt (Charlie Day), and Dale (Jason Sudekikis) can\'t leave their miserable hobs, so the cook up a creative strategy for eliminating their micromanaging and maniacal employers instead. Peculiar advice from a con artist sets the scheme in motion.");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(12, "Rock Star", 9.99, "Drama", "", "A Wannabe lead singer gets to live his wildest dream when he\'s whisked from anonymity to being the front man for the enormously popular band he worships. But he soon discovers that life in the fast lane isn\'t what he expected.");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(13, "Dirty Harry", 4.99, "Drama", "", "When a madman dubbed \"The Scorpio Killer\" terrorizes San Francisco, hard-boiled cop Harry Callahan (Clint Eastwood)--famous for his take-no-prisoners approach to law enforcement--is tasked with hunting down the psychopath.");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(14, "The Money Pit", 8.99, "Comedy", "", "An up-and-coming entertainment lawyer (Tom Hanks) and his yuppie girlfriend (Shelley Long) set out to renovate their dream house, only to be plagued by her ex-husband, an unscrupulous construction firm and the house\'s crumbling structure.");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(15, "Transcendence", 3.99, "Sci-Fi", "", "A husband and wife team of computer scientists work to advance artificial intelligence as a radical anti-technology organization fights to prevent them from creating a world where computers can transcend the abilities of the human brain.");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(16, "Pixels", 12.99, "Comedy", "", "After aliens attack Earth using 1980s arcade games as models for their onslaught, President Will Cooper (Kevin James) calls in longtime friend and former gaming ace Sam Brenner (Adam Sandler) to take on the extraterrestrial invaders.");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(17, "Spaceballs", 7.99, "Comedy", "", "In this spoof of the Star Wars trilogy, nefarious Dark Helmet (Rick Moranis) hatches a plan to snatch Princess Vespa (Daphne Zuniga) and steal her planet\'s air. Space bum Lone Star (Bill Pulman) and his clueless sidekick fly to the rescue, with help from Yogurt (Mel Brooks) and the power of \"The Schwartz.\"");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(18, "Raiders of the Lost Ark", 8.99, "Action Adventure", "", "When Dr. Indiana Jones (Harrison Ford)--the tweed-suited professor who just happens to be a celebrated archaeologist and adventurer hired by the government to locate the legendary Ark of the Covenant, he finds himself up against an entire Nazi Regime.");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(19, "Be Cool", 10.99, "Comedy", "", "Growing tired of the movie business, ex-loan shark Chili Palmer (John Travolta) sets his sights on the music business. His first client is singer who is on the lam from the Russian mob, and Chili finds himself resorting to his old tactics to fend them off.");
INSERT INTO movies.moviesTable VALUES(20, "Saving Private Ryan", 8.99, "Drama", "", "As U.S. troops storm the beaches of Normandy, three brothers lie dead on the battlefield, with a fourth trapped behind enemy lines. Captain John Miller (Tom Hanks) of the Army Rangers and seven of his men are ordered to penetrate German-held territory and bring the man home.");
